{"tid":1552541,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不分化 不割蓆 兄弟爬山 各自努力","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:07:06.000Z","uid":34816,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9e8c55d20eaa634c975e009472d3b3615d149d86","tid":1552541,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你班仆街到底重記唔記得呢四句由69引領我地到今日既格言啊？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地係咪真係咁易比班黑狗三毛帶風向啊？<br />\n<br />\n今日發生既事，起因都係班狗係中環亂拉人挑起衝突，想搞散今日個集會，你地重係到屌緊手足既可唔可以收一收皮，搞清楚前因後果先？<br />\n<br />\n今時今日，個運動發展到呢個地步，所有香港人早已團結一致，和勇早已結成一個不可分割既整體，除非係無差別殺害平民，邊撚有咁易失咩民氣啊，醒下啦，而家係全港抗共啊。"},{"pid":"4f8821af2979369a6a12976e65706b4257b8a555","tid":1552541,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc345071a2d307fb486b85e25c31c89a4bb2259","tid":1552541,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"文宣重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警意圖破壞示威者和平遊行</span>"},{"pid":"be09f8bfaac7d2a66e5bb6e1de6518f9cd08bb3f","tid":1552541,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"所有跟風屌手足既人反省下啦"},{"pid":"f4474908671dbffdd4b44ace7e1886e8c0c9700a","tid":1552541,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"b9d04c3cecc133dd036a25ce0e35cae8f87da724","tid":1552541,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8c55d20eaa634c975e009472d3b3615d149d86","tid":1552541,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你班仆街到底重記唔記得呢四句由69引領我地到今日既格言啊？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地係咪真係咁易比班黑狗三毛帶風向啊？<br />\n<br />\n今日發生